<A>__{ellie, used to not being taken seriously. turns back to the roar of the bush plane as it taxis down the strip. coming to a stop. she hurries over as the door swings open and... will dormer steps down. slipping on his sunglasses. scanning the nothingness around him. spots the swinging sign.}
<C>__{will}
<D>__{"halibut fishing capital of the world."}
